Cannot be Synchro Summoned. Must first be Special Summoned (from your Extra Deck) by Tributing 1 Tuner and 1 or more non-Tuner monsters you control, whose combined original DEF equal 2700. Once per turn (Quick Effect): You can target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; switch its ATK with this card's original ATK until the end of this turn. You can only use each of the following effects of "Lilia, Sylphale Whirlwind Paladin" once per turn, and cannot activate them in the same Chain. (Quick Effect): You can activate the appropriate effect based on this card's ATK;
● 0: This card cannot be destroyed by battle or card effects this turn.
● 100+: Target 1 card on the field; destroy it.
